Package: hcdb
Title: An R package for the High Court Database
Version: 1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Pat", "Leslie", , "patrick.leslie@anu.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9218-8981"))
Description: Provides easy access to the Australian High Court Database (HCDB), a structured
    dataset encoding all full judgments of the High Court of Australia from 1995 to 2020 and all
    special leave applications from 2003 to 2018. For details see Leslie et al. (2026)
    <doi:10.1177/2755323X261438254>.
